&s;ucce&s;s, if he minds his hits.'</Q></P>
<P> 
<Q REND="inline">'Well I hope you will mind yours,' &s;aid
Charles, 'but this you tell me of Mu&s;quito is a&s;toni&s;hing.'</Q> 
<Q REND="inline">'It is very true I a&s;&s;ure you,' an&s;wered
